    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_11_845-882",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "845-882",
      "markText": "英人初提香港的时候，北京还不知道香港在哪里。时人反对割地，不是反对割香港。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=845&rangeEnd=882",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=845&rangeEnd=882"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_11_2183-2224",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2183-2224",
      "markText": "不平等条约的根源，一部分由于我们的无知，一部分由于我们的法制未达到近代文明的水准。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2183&rangeEnd=2224",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2183&rangeEnd=2224"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_11_1663-1706",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1663-1706",
      "markText": "道光年间的中国人，完全不懂国际公法和国际形势，所以他们争所不当争，放弃所不应当放弃的。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1663&rangeEnd=1706",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1663&rangeEnd=1706"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_9_1010-1091",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1010-1091",
      "markText": "他屈服的方法很值得我们注意。他不是命令英国商人把烟交给林则徐，他是教英商把烟交给他，并且由他以商业监督的资格给各商收据，一转手之间，英商的鸦片变为大英帝国的鸦片。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1010&rangeEnd=1091",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1010&rangeEnd=1091"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_22_6025-6054",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "6025-6054",
      "markText": "严格说来，民众的迷信是我民族近代接受西洋文化的大阻碍之一。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=6025&rangeEnd=6054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=6025&rangeEnd=6054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_10_517-571",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "517-571",
      "markText": "从民族的历史看，鸦片战争的军事失败还不是民族致命伤。失败以后还不明了失败的理由力图改革，那才是民族的致命伤。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=517&rangeEnd=571",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=517&rangeEnd=571"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_45_782-841",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "782-841",
      "markText": "俄国没有费丝毫之力就得了八十万平方公里的土地，其对华外交的灵敏可说远在英国之上。而且俄国自始至终以中国的“朋友”自居！",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=782&rangeEnd=841",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=782&rangeEnd=841"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_16_1653-1679",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1653-1679",
      "markText": "他在岳州得到吴三桂留下来的军械，并抢夺了不少的帆船。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1653&rangeEnd=1679",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1653&rangeEnd=1679"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_9_2781-2861",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2781-2861",
      "markText": "道光帝高兴极了，觉得琦善以三寸之舌竟能说退英国的海陆军，远胜林则徐的孟浪多事。于是下令教内地各省的军队概归原防，“以节糜费”。同时革林则徐的职，教琦善去代替他。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2781&rangeEnd=2861",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2781&rangeEnd=2861"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_22_3620-3703",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "3620-3703",
      "markText": "夫天下之耻，莫耻于不若人……日本蕞尔小国尚知发愤为雄，独中国狃于因循积习，不思振作，耻孰甚焉？今不以不如人为耻，而独以学其人为耻，将安于不如，而终不学，遂可雪其耻乎？",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3620&rangeEnd=3703",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3620&rangeEnd=3703"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_23_3525-3604",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "3525-3604",
      "markText": "左宗棠的言论比较动听，李的比较合理；左是高调，李是低调。士大夫阶级一贯的尚感情，唱高调，当然拥护左宗棠。于是借外债，移用各省的建设费，以供左宗棠进攻新疆之用。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3525&rangeEnd=3604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=3525&rangeEnd=3604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_20_668-750",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "668-750",
      "markText": "并且实力充足，能为所欲为，但《北京条约》订了以后，英、法居然依据条约撤退军队，交还首都。时人认为这是了不得的事情，足证西洋人也守信义，所以对付外人并不是全无办法的。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=668&rangeEnd=750",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=668&rangeEnd=750"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_16_3756-3790",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "3756-3790",
      "markText": "私有的武力是太平天国内乱的意外副产品，以后我们要深切地注意它的出世。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3756&rangeEnd=3790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3756&rangeEnd=3790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_23_2402-2460",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "2402-2460",
      "markText": "据我们所知，历史上各种政体，君主也好，民主也好，各种社会经济制度，资本主义也好，封建主义也好，都有行帝国主义的可能。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2402&rangeEnd=2460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2402&rangeEnd=2460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_26_3262-3297",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "3262-3297",
      "markText": "这种瓜分运动就是甲午的败仗引起来的。在近代的世界，败仗是千万不能打的。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=3262&rangeEnd=3297",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=3262&rangeEnd=3297"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_5_1182-1218",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1182-1218",
      "markText": "西洋人养成了热烈的爱国心，深刻的民族观念。我们则死守着家族观念和家乡观念",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1182&rangeEnd=1218",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1182&rangeEnd=1218"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_13_4550-4647",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4550-4647",
      "markText": "英使到北京后，必须向中国皇帝面递国书。这是国际间应行的礼节，但那时中国人认为这是外夷的狂悖，其居心叵测，中国绝不能容忍。载垣乃令军队捕拿英、法代表到通州来的交涉人员。这一举激怒外人，军事又起了。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4550&rangeEnd=4647",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4550&rangeEnd=4647"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26797274_28_4336-4380",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "4336-4380",
      "markText": "李鸿章主张接受俄国的要求，但是幸而他在辛丑的冬天死了，不然东北三省就要在他手里送给俄国了",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26797274&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4336&rangeEnd=4380",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b932b707198e4da6b9f742?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=4336&rangeEnd=4380"
    },
    {
